{"tid":2329065,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[撐蘋果] 黎智英遭加控｜美國列黎智英為「宗教良心犯」 促釋放黎智英黃之鋒周庭","createTime":"2020-12-17T03:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T06:14:33.000Z","uid":6845,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f7370e070160414ae5a73b7363ffbe2d814db5","tid":2329065,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Mx3DH2v0seY4wJByNPPWrwCYOc0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2TVDA5CF7VHJLDKR6U4RQYVNXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMx3DH2v0seY4wJByNPPWrwCYOc0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2TVDA5CF7VHJLDKR6U4RQYVNXQ.jpg&h=a05321ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">美國國際宗教自由委員會（USCIRF）把黎智英列入宗教良心犯名單。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英早前遭加控涉港版國安法控罪，目前仍被扣押。美國國際宗教自由委員會（USCIRF）周三發聲明，表示會把黎智英列入「宗教良心犯」（Religious Prisoners of Conscience）名單，要求中方釋放黎智英及其他因爭取人權、民主及宗教自由而被拘禁的人士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201217/J4AASI2HABHSBP3TEY4GR2T6A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201217%2FJ4AASI2HABHSBP3TEY4GR2T6A4%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28dG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=29dfe26c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201217%2FJ4AASI2HABHSBP3TEY4GR2T6A4%2F&h=a2b18efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201217/J4AASI2HABHSBP3TEY4GR2T6A4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8折訂閱蘋果，一日都係1.33$，7-11都可以俾錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200726/IPDXZJHXU3FCPOLZSSNBWUYED4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FIPDXZJHXU3FCPOLZSSNBWUYED4%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28dG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=98681d78\" data-ef-ur